ar, couple of fun items I still want to camp, trying all the DoN missions at least once, doing a tipt trial, do all the MPG group trials, and finishing off as many DoD missions as I can.  That's just for starters. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Needless to say, I see things differently.  There has been a massive increase in casual content and greater rewards for said content.  I think when I hit 70 I had just under 3k unbuffed hp, and after a lot of work, I just broke 6k unbuffed, and my sights are now set on 7k.  I don't even have PoR yet, so the list of things to do will only grow once I get off my lazy butt and buy it.&lt;br&gt;</description>
